This isn’t some cookie-cutter influencer program.

We don’t just hand out discount codes. We build elite warriors.

You’ll get training, mentorship, and the tools to grow mentally, personally, and financially.

Learn the products. Master the game. Grow your following.

settings.heading: How do I make money as part of the team?
settings.row_content: You’ll receive a custom code or affiliate link that earns you commission on every sale you generate. The more you grow and convert, the more you earn and higher-level opportunities open up as you prove yourself.

settings.heading: Do you provide any training or resources to help me succeed?
settings.row_content: Yes. We equip every team member with the tools to win, including product education, content tips, coaching calls, and direct communication with our team. You won’t just rep a brand, you’ll be mentored, guided, and backed at every level.

settings.heading: Can I still apply if I’ve never been sponsored or part of a brand before?
settings.row_content: 100%. We’re not here for the “polished industry athlete.” We’re looking for raw talent, real stories, and relentless effort. If you’re hungry, we’ll help you every way that we can.

settings.heading: What kind of content are you looking for from athletes?
settings.row_content: Authenticity. We want content that reflects your lifestyle, gym footage, real transformations, product education, personal stories, and behind-the-scenes hustle. No fake personas, just real people pushing products trying to make a real impact on people's lives.

settings.heading: If selected, what are the expectations as part of the team?
settings.row_content: Show up. Represent the brand with integrity. Stay active on social media. Engage with the mission and your fellow teammates. This isn’t just a code, it’s a message that we are trying to push forward, and we expect everyone on the roster to carry that weight and support with pride.
